output.analysis:
Let me analyze this post according to the given criteria:
1. Has CMF: No CMF number is present in this post.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, it directly mentions "Marcel Ciolacu", who is a presidential candidate (Position 3 - PSD).
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid advertisement on Facebook and Instagram, targeting a potential audience of 100,001-500,000 people, with actual impressions between 10,000-14,999.
4. Electoral objective: Yes. The post portrays Marcel Ciolacu in a leadership context ("Lider, strateg, antrenor") and uses the metaphor of "Champions League" to suggest he's at the highest level of performance. This is clearly meant to build a positive image during the electoral period.
5. Journalism: No, this is not journalistic content. It's a promotional message without any informative value.
6. Personal opinion: No, this is a paid party advertisement from PSD Dolj, not a personal opinion.
The post is clearly electoral propaganda as it: - Directly names a presidential candidate - Is paid advertising - Has clear electoral messaging - Aims to influence public opinion - Is published by a party organization (PSD Dolj)

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It directly promotes a presidential candidate (Marcel Ciolacu) - Uses metaphorical language to enhance his image - Is paid advertising with significant reach - Comes from an official party source (PSD Dolj) - Has clear electoral messaging intent
conclusion.message-for-police: PSD Dolj, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin publicarea și promovarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorală după încheierea perioadei de campanie, respectiv după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Postarea cu ID-ul 1736664547156289 il promovează direct pe candidatul prezidențial Marcel Ciolacu, folosind termeni laudativi precum "Lider, strateg, antrenor" și analogii sportive ("Champions League") pentru a-i construi o imagine pozitivă și a influența preferințele electorale ale votanților. Postarea este sponsorizată, având un buget între 100-199 RON și un impact semnificativ de 10.000-14.999 impresii, demonstrând intenția clară de a influența procesul electoral în afara perioadei legale de campanie.
